    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233250/extras/68b61ff488cd0463fc254536abcfe7a4.webp?t=1761240405\" width=600 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>IslaNode: Rescue Signal</strong> takes players on a survival adventure like no other, set on a deserted island with nothing but natural resources and your wits. Stranded alone, you’ll need to explore, gather materials, and use a unique node-based crafting system to transform basic elements into survival tools. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233250/extras/60b37c153ace2361c74ef1cc75c44872.webp?t=1761240405\" width=600 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine world resources to craft.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233250/extras/8dbe6a9cecaa029ca3e602ab90ad7fe6.poster.avif?t=1761240405\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233250/extras/8dbe6a9cecaa029ca3e602ab90ad7fe6.webm?t=1761240405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233250/extras/8dbe6a9cecaa029ca3e602ab90ad7fe6.mp4?t=1761240405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233250/extras/759a13d05418ee81222879f982309024.webp?t=1761240405\" width=600 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Building allows you to create more complex shapes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233250/extras/266982ecd16d07c903faf280fcc5556e.poster.avif?t=1761240405\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233250/extras/266982ecd16d07c903faf280fcc5556e.webm?t=1761240405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233250/extras/266982ecd16d07c903faf280fcc5556e.mp4?t=1761240405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233250/extras/b43666b04e39b015a6f145b4e34c6cb3.webp?t=1761240405\" width=600 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233250/extras/ed875bd2d641ddf132eba5730967fcc7.poster.avif?t=1761240405\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233250/extras/ed875bd2d641ddf132eba5730967fcc7.webm?t=1761240405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3233250/extras/ed875bd2d641ddf132eba5730967fcc7.mp4?t=1761240405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The ultimate goal? Construct a towering lighthouse to signal for help and secure your escape. Each resource you gather, from wood to stone, plays a crucial role in building a sturdy, weather-resistant tower as you face the challenges of the island environment. With vibrant, cartoony visuals and an intuitive crafting interface, <i><strong>IslaNode</strong></i> combines the thrill of survival with the satisfaction of creative construction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
